Schwarzer-Adler-Platz Am 7. Mai 2015 feierte der Karl-Holoubek-Hof sein 40-jähriges Bestehen. Besucht wurde das Fest auch von Wohnbaustadtrat Michael Ludwig, Bezirksvorsteher Gerhard Zatlokal und seiner Stellvertreterin Merja Biedermann.  Im Rahmen des Festes wurde der Platz vor der VHS15 umbenannt. MieterInnen und AnrainerInnen hatten die Möglichkeit, Namensvorschläge einzureichen, eine Jury wählt anschließend aus den rund 40 Einreichungen fünf aus. Schließlich stimmten die BewohnerInnen sowie AnrainerInnen für den Namen 'Schwarzer-Adler-Platz'.
Veterinary in the middle of the sea :) https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/3642788696
closing_comment: I've now moved the node to a place more sensible on land (I bet the API that created the note removed the fractional digits from the coordinate and placed it at 44.0, 14.0...) with https://www.openstreetmap.org/changeset/142170908. Put a fixme on it, but given the abysmal state of OSM coverage there I doubt it will be fixed anytime soon ;-) Thanks for pointing this node out, wouldn't have found it without your note!

Business Name: Pod Outdoor   https://podoutdoor.com   Pod Outdoor is your online destination for outdoor gear. Our goal is to help you find everything you need for your next outside adventure at great prices. We look for innovative new products as well as classic gear to ensure you get the most out of your hunting, fishing and camping excursions.  Pod Outdoor is also the U.S. home of the Tetra-Pod, which is the only enclosed trailer in North America that can be converted into a boat. The Tetra-Pod comes in both Off Road and On Road versions that are designed for both work and play, and it only takes a couple of minutes to switch from one mode to the other.  If you have any questions about an order or about any of our products, please contact us by chat in the bottom left hand corner of our site or via the email form on our contact page. You can also reach us by phone Monday through Friday 9AM-5PM EST at (417) 237-0129.
